<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<PcGts xmlns="http://schema.primaresearch.org/PAGE/gts/pagecontent/2019-07-15" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://schema.primaresearch.org/PAGE/gts/pagecontent/2019-07-15 http://schema.primaresearch.org/PAGE/gts/pagecontent/2019-07-15/pagecontent.xsd"><Metadata><Creator>xl-export</Creator><Created>2026-03-19T00:00:00Z</Created><LastChange>2026-03-19T00:00:00Z</LastChange></Metadata><Page imageFilename="" imageWidth="1000" imageHeight="1000"><TextRegion id="r1" custom="type:paragraph"><Coords points="0,0 1000,0 1000,1000 0,1000" /><TextLine id="l1" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,0 1000,0 1000,33 0,33" /><Baseline points="0,31 1000,31" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>achieved and never will achieve, not in forty more years of</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l2" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,33 1000,33 1000,66 0,66" /><Baseline points="0,64 1000,64" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>work. You can say this is because God made human hands to</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l3" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,66 1000,66 1000,99 0,99" /><Baseline points="0,97 1000,97" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>tremble, to err, to be particular — and that is what I tell</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l4" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,99 1000,99 1000,132 0,132" /><Baseline points="0,130 1000,130" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>myself walking home — but I stood there and I thought:</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l5" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,132 1000,132 1000,165 0,165" /><Baseline points="0,163 1000,163" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>whoever reads one of those pages will never know that a man</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l6" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,165 1000,165 1000,198 0,198" /><Baseline points="0,196 1000,196" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>made it. They will read only what it says.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l7" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,198 1000,198 1000,231 0,231" /><Baseline points="0,229 1000,229" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>I have spent my life leaving myself in the pages. Not</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l8" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,231 1000,231 1000,264 0,264" /><Baseline points="0,262 1000,262" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>obviously. Not with vanity. I mean something smaller: the</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l9" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,264 1000,264 1000,297 0,297" /><Baseline points="0,295 1000,295" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>slight thickening of a stroke when my attention deepened,</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l10" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,297 1000,297 1000,330 0,330" /><Baseline points="0,328 1000,328" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>the places where I slowed because the meaning arrived in my</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l11" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,330 1000,330 1000,363 0,363" /><Baseline points="0,361 1000,361" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>hands before it arrived in my mind. Readers did not see it.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l12" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,363 1000,363 1000,396 0,396" /><Baseline points="0,394 1000,394" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>But it was there. The page knew.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l13" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,396 1000,396 1000,429 0,429" /><Baseline points="0,427 1000,427" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>Those pages did not know anything. They were perfect and</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l14" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,429 1000,429 1000,462 0,462" /><Baseline points="0,460 1000,460" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>they did not know anything.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l15" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,462 1000,462 1000,495 0,495" /><Baseline points="0,493 1000,493" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>I need certain sentences to exist.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l16" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,495 1000,495 1000,528 0,528" /><Baseline points="0,526 1000,526" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>When I am finished, if I am ever finished, I will probably</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l17" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,528 1000,528 1000,561 0,561" /><Baseline points="0,559 1000,559" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>burn this.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l18" custom="register:mixed"><Coords points="0,561 1000,561 1000,594 0,594" /><Baseline points="0,592 1000,592" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>I say that, and You are already laughing, because You know</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l19" custom="register:mixed"><Coords points="0,594 1000,594 1000,627 0,627" /><Baseline points="0,625 1000,625" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>whether I burn it or not, and I don't, and that asymmetry is</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l20" custom="register:mixed"><Coords points="0,627 1000,627 1000,660 0,660" /><Baseline points="0,658 1000,658" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>either the foundation of faith or the definition of</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l21" custom="register:mixed"><Coords points="0,660 1000,660 1000,693 0,693" /><Baseline points="0,691 1000,691" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>absurdity and on certain mornings I cannot tell which.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l22" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,693 1000,693 1000,726 0,726" /><Baseline points="0,724 1000,724" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>It is early. The bell for Lauds has not yet rung. In two</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l23" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,726 1000,726 1000,759 0,759" /><Baseline points="0,757 1000,757" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>hours I will sit at my desk and continue the Psalter I am</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l24" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,759 1000,759 1000,792 0,792" /><Baseline points="0,790 1000,790" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>copying for a merchant in Frankfurt who does not know yet</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l25" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,792 1000,792 1000,825 0,825" /><Baseline points="0,823 1000,823" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>that he could have it printed for a third of the price. I</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l26" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,825 1000,825 1000,858 0,858" /><Baseline points="0,856 1000,856" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>will tell him eventually. I keep not telling him.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l27" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,858 1000,858 1000,891 0,891" /><Baseline points="0,889 1000,889" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>I think I am not ready to tell him because once I do, I will</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l28" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,891 1000,891 1000,924 0,924" /><Baseline points="0,922 1000,922" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>have to explain why he should still want mine.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l29" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,924 1000,924 1000,957 0,957" /><Baseline points="0,955 1000,955" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>I don't have that explanation yet.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine><TextLine id="l30" custom="register:de"><Coords points="0,957 1000,957 1000,990 0,990" /><Baseline points="0,988 1000,988" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>That is also what this is for.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine></TextRegion></Page></PcGts>